    Java class for columns element declaration.

    Each connectoid represents a potential point of exit/entry from/to the physical network coming from the zone/centroid.
    XMLElementConnectoids
    Connectoids are the interface between supply and demand which are defined as a node (but in practice create virtual links (connectors) between the centroid and physical road network).
    XMLElementCsvdata
    Java class for csvdata element declaration.
    XMLElementDemandConfiguration
    Java class for demandconfiguration element declaration.
    XMLElementDuration
    Duration is a positive integer (in seconds) and we start counting from the start time.

    Each mode can have a description(name) and pcu value besides their unique identifier (id).
    XMLElementNodes

    Java class for anonymous complex type.
